A1 Diesel is a global leader in diesel injector and
turbocharger remanufacturing, trusted by over 50,000
customers throughout 60+ countries. Since its founding
in 2012, A1 Diesel has actually earned a reputation for
precision, reliability, and professional service. With a
group of extremely experienced service technicians and a
cutting-edge BOSCH computer stand, the company offers
comprehensive diagnostics and dependable repairs for
trucks, cars, and specialised machinery.

An authorised Bosch dealer, A1 Diesel integrates
innovative innovation with decades of hands-on
experience to restore engine performance and prolong
vehicle lifespan. Whether you own a business fleet or a
high-performance diesel vehicle, A1 Diesel provides
tailored solutions developed to satisfy the greatest
industry requirements, with a tried and tested 99.9%
customer fulfillment rate to back it up.
